race.comment: STABILIZER (7) has been knocking on the door of a maiden victory with consecutive placings in town and should be cherry-ripe for this fourth run back from a spell. Looks the one they all have to run down. CANTANKEROUS (1) has hit the top four in four of five career outings and this is not an overly strong affair. Looms as the main danger while fresh. ROCHEDALE HERO (6) is facing the starter for the first time but is sure to be well-educated from the Bruce barn. Bold showing likely. DAWSON DIRECTOR (2) gets the deadly Gollan/Lang combination and any push in betting must be noted. ASTERN EFFORT (8) best of the rest with the claim.
